{"text_id":42931,"tokens":["##"," The"," Electoral"," College",":"," A"," Compromise"," With"," Fla","ws","\n\n","The"," Electoral"," College"," system"," in"," the"," United"," States"," stands"," as"," a"," controversial"," anomaly"," in"," a"," democracy"," where"," the"," popular"," vote"," ostensibly"," reigns"," supreme","."," While"," lauded"," for"," preventing"," frivolous"," elections"," and"," fostering"," compromise",","," the"," system"," suffers"," from"," inherent"," disadvantages",","," potentially"," undermining"," the"," very"," values"," it"," aims"," to"," uphold","."," The"," persistent"," tension"," between"," public"," will"," and"," electoral"," outcomes"," demands"," a"," thorough"," examination"," of"," its"," efficacy"," and"," potential"," for"," reform",".","\n\n","The"," proponents"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," highlight"," its"," ability"," to"," prevent"," \"","popular"," tyranny","\""," by"," ensuring"," larger"," states"," do"," not"," dominate"," elections","."," By"," allocating"," more"," electors"," to"," populous"," states",","," the"," system"," effectively"," gives"," a"," voice"," to"," rural"," and"," less"," populated"," areas","."," This"," concern"," is"," particularly"," relevant"," in"," the"," current"," political"," climate",","," where"," a"," candidate"," could"," win"," the"," presidency"," despite"," losing"," the"," popular"," vote",","," as"," seen"," in"," ","2","0","0","0","."," However",","," this"," very"," feature"," can"," undermine"," public"," faith"," in"," the"," democratic"," process",","," leading"," to"," feelings"," of"," alienation"," and"," dis","enf","ranch","isement",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," the"," current"," system"," disproportion","ately"," empowers"," certain"," regions"," at"," the"," expense"," of"," others","."," Small"," states"," receive"," an"," out","sized"," number"," of"," electors"," despite"," their"," demographic"," and"," economic"," significance","."